### v1.5.9
#### NEW FEATURES
- added option to show rough estimated **time to kill (TTK)** for bosses (settings > live meter)
- search now supports multiple words. example: player1 player2
- improved method to save app crash logs to file

#### BUG FIXES
- fixed optimize database function not working

thanks to [@JonasHri](https://github.com/JonasHri), [@yamiM0NSTER](https://github.com/yamiM0NSTER) for the contributions

full patch notes on [github](https://github.com/snoww/loa-logs/releases/latest)

send bug reports/suggestions to [#loa-logs](https://discord.gg/sbSa3pkDF5)
